<item>
            <title>[AMQ-4995] Runtime Configuration Plugin - reapply destination interceptor after reload</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AMQ-4995</link>
                <project id="12311210" key="AMQ">ActiveMQ Classic</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When we change destination interceptor we need to reapply it to all destination as otherwise the effects will have no change. An example is changing property like &quot;forwardOnly&quot; in the following configuration&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;destinationInterceptors&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;virtualDestinationInterceptor&amp;gt;
       &amp;lt;virtualDestinations&amp;gt;
           &amp;lt;compositeQueue forwardOnly=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;&quot;&lt;/span&gt; name=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;VirtualDestination.CompositeQueue&quot;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;
               &amp;lt;forwardTo&amp;gt;
                   &amp;lt;queue physicalName=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;VirtualDestination.QueueConsumer&quot;&lt;/span&gt;/&amp;gt;
                   &amp;lt;topic physicalName=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;VirtualDestination.TopicConsumer&quot;&lt;/span&gt;/&amp;gt;
               &amp;lt;/forwardTo&amp;gt;
           &amp;lt;/compositeQueue&amp;gt;
       &amp;lt;/virtualDestinations&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;/virtualDestinationInterceptor&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;/destinationInterceptors&amp;gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
